			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2683092">
									

<p>So this is a project that I've thought about for a long time, and with staff now looking at the Secure Facilities page, I thought this was as good a time as any to pull it back out of the bag and see what we could come up with.</p>
<p>Since I write a <em>lot</em> about Site-81, here's where I started. Depending on interest, and what the staff project comes up with, we may try to do a few more of these. Who knows. Call it world-building.</p>
<p>Anyway, hope you enjoy!</p>

